    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "::: {.grid}\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.g-col-12 .g-col-md-5}\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.story-section}\n",
        "\n",
        "## El problema que nadie nombra correctamente\n",
        "\n",
        "En México hablamos de **rezago educativo** como si fuera un problema de escuelas.\n",
        "Hablamos de **desnutrición infantil** como si fuera un problema de alimentos.\n",
        "\n",
        "Pero la neurociencia nos dice algo diferente:\n",
        "\n",
        "> Cuando un niño crece en pobreza extrema, con desnutrición crónica y exposición\n",
        "> a violencia, su corteza prefrontal se desarrolla de manera distinta.\n",
        "> No es metáfora. Es anatomía.\n",
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.story-section}\n",
        "Este tablero cruza datos oficiales de INEGI, CONEVAL, SEP y ENSANUT para\n",
        "mostrar dónde en México ese daño es más probable — y por qué los ODS 3 y 4\n",
        "son, en realidad, el mismo problema.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## ¿Qué es el Índice de Vulnerabilidad Neuroeducativa?\n",
        "\n",
        "El **IVN** es un índice compuesto que integra cuatro dimensiones:\n",
        "\n",
        "| Dimensión | Peso | Fuente |\n",
        "|---|---|---|\n",
        "| Rezago educativo | 30% | SEP 2022 |\n",
        "| Desnutrición infantil | 30% | ENSANUT 2022 |\n",
        "| Pobreza extrema | 25% | CONEVAL 2022 |\n",
        "| Población 0-4 años | 15% | INEGI 2020 |\n",
        "\n",
        "Los pesos reflejan la jerarquía causal: la desnutrición y el rezago son causas directas de alteración prefrontal.\n",
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.g-col-12 .g-col-md-7 .sticky-column}"
      ],
      "id": "327e572f"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| label: mapa-ivn\n",
        "#| fig-cap: Índice de Vulnerabilidad Neuroeducativa por estado\n",
        "\n",
        "# 1. Preparar datos\n",
        "df[\"cve_str\"] = df[\"cve_estado\"].astype(str).str.zfill(2)\n",
        "\n",
        "# 2. Crear el mapa interactivo\n",
        "fig1 = px.choropleth(\n",
        "    df,\n",
        "    geojson=\"[https://raw.githubusercontent.com/isaacarroyov/data_viz_practice/main/Python/visualizations-from-tweets/2022/2022-05_30DayChartChallenge/data/estados_mexico.geojson](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/isaacarroyov/data_viz_practice/main/Python/visualizations-from-tweets/2022/2022-05_30DayChartChallenge/data/estados_mexico.geojson)\",\n",
        "    locations=\"cve_str\",\n",
        "    featureidkey=\"properties.CVE_ENT\",\n",
        "    color=\"IVN\",\n",
        "    hover_name=\"estado\",\n",
        "    hover_data={\n",
        "        \"IVN\": \":.1f\",\n",
        "        \"nivel_urgencia\": True,\n",
        "        \"rezago_educativo_pct\": \":.1f\",\n",
        "        \"desnutricion_cronica_pct\": \":.1f\",\n",
        "        \"pobreza_extrema_pct\": \":.1f\",\n",
        "        \"cve_str\": False,\n",
        "    },\n",
        "    color_continuous_scale=[\n",
        "        [0.0, \"#1D3557\"],\n",
        "        [0.3, \"#A8DADC\"],\n",
        "        [0.6, \"#F4A261\"],\n",
        "        [1.0, \"#E63946\"],\n",
        "    ],\n",
        "    labels={\n",
        "        \"IVN\": \"IVN\",\n",
        "        \"nivel_urgencia\": \"Nivel\",\n",
        "        \"rezago_educativo_pct\": \"Rezago educ. (%)\",\n",
        "        \"desnutricion_cronica_pct\": \"Desnutrición (%)\",\n",
        "        \"pobreza_extrema_pct\": \"Pobreza extrema (%)\",\n",
        "    },\n",
        "    title=\"El Cerebro Vulnerable — IVN por estado\",\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "# 3. Estilo y Layout\n",
        "fig1.update_geos(fitbounds=\"locations\", visible=False, bgcolor=C_FONDO)\n",
        "fig1.update_layout(\n",
        "    **TEMPLATE,\n",
        "    coloraxis_colorbar=dict(\n",
        "        title=\"IVN\",\n",
        "        tickvals=[0, 25, 50, 75, 100],\n",
        "        ticktext=[\"Bajo\", \"Moderado\", \"Medio\", \"Alto\", \"Crítico\"],\n",
        "    ),\n",
        "    margin=dict(l=0, r=0, t=60, b=0),\n",
        "    height=600,\n",
        ")\n",
        "fig1.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "Los pesos **no son arbitrarios** — reflejan la jerarquía causal establecida\n",
        "en la literatura de neurociencias del desarrollo. La desnutrición y el rezago\n",
        "tienen el mismo peso porque ambos son causas directas de alteración prefrontal,\n",
        "no consecuencias.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## El mapa de la vulnerabilidad\n",
        "\n",
        "```{python}\n",
        "#| label: mapa-ivn\n",
        "#| fig-cap: \"Índice de Vulnerabilidad Neuroeducativa por estado — a mayor valor, mayor riesgo de daño neurológico diferencial\"\n",
        "\n",
        "df[\"cve_str\"] = df[\"cve_estado\"].astype(str).str.zfill(2)\n",
        "\n",
        "fig1 = px.choropleth(\n",
        "    df,\n",
        "    geojson=(\n",
        "        \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/isaacarroyov/data_viz_practice/\"\n",
        "        \"main/Python/visualizations-from-tweets/2022/2022-05_30DayChartChallenge/\"\n",
        "        \"data/estados_mexico.geojson\"\n",
        "    ),\n",
        "    locations=\"cve_str\",\n",
        "    featureidkey=\"properties.CVE_ENT\",\n",
        "    color=\"IVN\",\n",
        "    hover_name=\"estado\",\n",
        "    hover_data={\n",
        "        \"IVN\": \":.1f\",\n",
        "        \"nivel_urgencia\": True,\n",
        "        \"rezago_educativo_pct\": \":.1f\",\n",
        "        \"desnutricion_cronica_pct\": \":.1f\",\n",
        "        \"pobreza_extrema_pct\": \":.1f\",\n",
        "        \"cve_str\": False,\n",
        "    },\n",
        "    color_continuous_scale=[\n",
        "        [0.0, \"#1D3557\"],\n",
        "        [0.3, \"#A8DADC\"],\n",
        "        [0.6, \"#F4A261\"],\n",
        "        [1.0, \"#E63946\"],\n",
        "    ],\n",
        "    labels={\n",
        "        \"IVN\": \"IVN\",\n",
        "        \"nivel_urgencia\": \"Nivel\",\n",
        "        \"rezago_educativo_pct\": \"Rezago educ. (%)\",\n",
        "        \"desnutricion_cronica_pct\": \"Desnutrición (%)\",\n",
        "        \"pobreza_extrema_pct\": \"Pobreza extrema (%)\",\n",
        "    },\n",
        "    title=\"El Cerebro Vulnerable — IVN por estado\",\n",
        ")\n",
        "fig1.update_geos(fitbounds=\"locations\", visible=False, bgcolor=C_FONDO)\n",
        "fig1.update_layout(\n",
        "    **TEMPLATE,\n",
        "    coloraxis_colorbar=dict(\n",
        "        title=\"IVN\",\n",
        "        tickvals=[0, 25, 50, 75, 100],\n",
        "        ticktext=[\"Bajo\", \"Moderado\", \"Medio\", \"Alto\", \"Crítico\"],\n",
        "    ),\n",
        "    margin=dict(l=0, r=0, t=60, b=0),\n",
        "    height=520,\n",
        ")\n",
        "fig1.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "::: "
      ],
      "id": "mapa-ivn",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
